      "para_id": "Q001118.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) For Ninĝirsu of the E-ninnu , En-metena , ruler of Lagaš , child of En-ana-tum , ruler of Lagaš , built his temple , decorated it with gold and silver , and embellished it with inscribed clay nails ."
    }
